General Assembly Senate Resolution No. 5
February Session, 2026 LCO No. 2213
Referred to Committee on EXECUTIVE AND LEGISLATIVE
NOMINATIONS
Introduced by:
SEN. DUFF, 25th Dist.
RESOLUTION CONFIRMING THE NOMINATION OF WAKANA HIROTA
OF BERLIN TO BE A MEMBER OF THE PSYCHIATRIC SECURITY
REVIEW BOARD.
Resolved by the Senate:
1 That the nomination by His Excellency, the Governor, of Wakana
2 Hirota of Berlin, to be a member of the Psychiatric Security Review
3 Board, as a member of the general public with substantial experience in
4 victim advocacy, in succession to Ranesha L. Nichols, to serve a term
5 ending June 30, 2028, or until a successor is appointed and has qualified,
6 whichever is longer, is hereby approved and confirmed.
LCO No. 2213 1 of 1

